  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "SALES PROMOTER (SMALL APPLIANCES)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Primary Function</strong></p><ul><li>To be sales driven and customer oriented and increase product sales</li><li>To raise awareness of product and build customer’s interest.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Main Duties and Responsibilities</strong></p><p><strong>1. Daily Scope of job:</strong></p><ul><li>Actively Promote item such as oven, vacuum cleaner and cooking appliances to customers.</li><li>Present product features, benefits, and technical specifications to customers.</li><li>Build strong relationships with customers to drive product awareness and sales.</li><li>Work in dynamic environments such as departmental store and atriums.</li><li>Achieve monthly sales target to earn attractive incentives and commissions</li><li>Collaborate with sales team to achieve targets</li></ul><p><br /><strong>2. Weekly/Monthly Scope of Job:</strong></p><ul><li>Participate in new product training and development activities to update skills and knowledge.</li><li>Monthly sales meeting in office</li></ul><p><strong>3. Others:</strong></p><ul><li>Require wearing uniform in neat and pleasant appearance.</li><li>Always perform a pleasant and patient attitude to customers.</li></ul><p><strong>4.</strong> Any other duties which may be assigned from time to time.</p><p><br /><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Able to commit weekdays and weekends. (6 days workweek)</li><li>Enthusiastic and comfortable engaging with customers.</li><li>Sales-driven, with a passion for promoting quality products.</li><li>Willingness to work in different retail environments.</li><li>A team player who is proactive and highly motivated.</li></ul>",
